ansparency, safety, and resource accessibility.\n\n**[Question 5] - What are the key components of my approach and results?**\nThe proposed methodology involves developing a transparent fine-tuning framework that includes safety-specific data annotation, iterative evaluations, and cost-effective computational solutions. The expected outcomes include a reproducible fine-tuning process for open-source LLMs that improves safety and usability, making them more accessible to the broader community."}

